A
B
Uncertain

Decision rule:

return A if description_A is the stronger match
return B if description_B is the stronger match
return Uncertain if there is not enough difference to prefer one over the other

Constraints:

return exactly one token-like label
no explanation
no reasoning
no extra words
no formatting

